    participant CL as Claude API

    U->>C: Submit Task
    C->>H: Route Task
    H->>H: Classify Task
    H->>O: Health Check
    O-->>H: Healthy
    H-->>C: Route to Ollama

    C->>G: Generate Code
    G->>G: Build Context
    G->>O: Generate Request
    O-->>G: Stream Response
    G-->>C: Generated Code

    C->>R: Review Code
    R->>CL: Review Request
    CL-->>R: Review Result
    R->>R: Parse Decision
    R-->>C: APPROVE

    C-->>U: Final Code
```

### Iteration Scenario

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Ollama
    participant G as Code Generator
    participant R as Code Reviewer
    participant CL as Claude API
    participant RL as Review Loop

    RL->>G: Generate (Iteration 1)
    G->>O: Generate Request
    O-->>G: Code V1
    G-->>RL: Save Iteration 1

    RL->>R: Review V1
    R->>CL: Review Request
    CL-->>R: Issues Found
    R-->>RL: ITERATE + Feedback

    RL->>G: Regenerate (Iteration 2)
    Note over G: Include Feedback
    G->>O: Generate Request
    O-->>G: Code V2
    G-->>RL: Save Iteration 2

    RL->>R: Review V2
    R->>CL: Review Request
    CL-->>R: Still Issues
    R-->>RL: ITERATE + Feedback

    RL->>G: Regenerate (Iteration 3)
    Note over G: Include Feedback
    G->>O: Generate Request
    O-->>G: Code V3
    G-->>RL: Save Iteration 3

    RL->>R: Review V3
    R->>CL: Review Request
    CL-->>R: Looks Good
    R-->>RL: APPROVE

    RL-->>G: Return Approved Code
